window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jason loves his life as a stay-at-home dad, but being a divorced single father wasn't part of the plan.</b></p> <p>Besides his kids, pies are his passion. He makes and sells his creations at the Heartcraft Market, but it's not enough to live off of.</p> <p>After his father's recent health scare, Nico is determined to help revive their family diner. Then he meets Jason, whose pies are as sweet as he is, and an idea begins to form.</p> <p>Jason's kids are everything to him, but his bed feels empty at night. Nico has always wanted a family, but he has yet to find a man that he could build a life with. Can a few pies lead to the promise of a future together?</p> <p><i>Pies &amp; Promises</i> features two men whose love for family and food brings them together and has plenty of heart and heat baked in. The Heartcraft Market series features interconnected standalone novels that can be enjoyed on their own.</p>"; 
